  <div class="c-product-widget__product">
      <div class="c-product-widget__vanity-container">
        <img alt="Product image of Goplus 3-in-1 Treadmill Desk" eager="false" class="lazyload blur-up " data-src="https://reviewed-com-res.cloudinary.com/image/fetch/s--Naqy2HI3--/b_white,c_fit,cs_srgb,f_auto,fl_progressive.strip_profile,g_center,h_150,q_auto,w_375/https://reviewed-production.s3.amazonaws.com/1655145318581/goplus-3-in-1.jpeg" style="aspect-ratio: 1.0;" src="https://reviewed-com-res.cloudinary.com/image/fetch/s--48rpMxTQ--/b_white,c_fit,cs_srgb,f_auto,fl_progressive.strip_profile,g_center,h_150,q_1,w_375/https://reviewed-production.s3.amazonaws.com/1655145318581/goplus-3-in-1.jpeg">
      </div>

    <div class="c-product-widget__text-container">
      <div class="u2 c-product-widget__name">
        Goplus 3-in-1 Treadmill Desk
      </div>

      <div class="c-product-widget__content">
      <ul>
<li>
<strong>Max speed:</strong> Up to 7.5 mph</li>
<li>
<strong>Weight limit:</strong> 220 lbs</li>
</ul>

<p>This desk has a lot of convenient features that aim to improve both your work rhythm and health. You can use the large LCD screen or the remote control to track your speed, distance, calories burned, activity time, and steps. In addition, the screen has a spot for you to place your phone or computer, which can be hooked up for you to listen to music while you get in a little extra physical activity during your workday. This treadmill absorbs shock and has a thick, 16-inch-wide layer belt to reduce noise as you move anywhere between 0.5 and 7.5 miles per hour.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      <div class="pros-cons">
    <div class="pros">
      <h4 class="pros-cons__title">Pros</h4>
      <ul class="pros-cons__list">
          <li class="pros-cons__list-item">
            <p class="pros-cons__text">
              Built-in wheels for portability
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="pros-cons__list-item">
            <p class="pros-cons__text">
              Data-monitoring LCD screen
